    "en": {
      "title": "Rs.1648 crore spent on printing books",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Ministry of Education, it is expected to spend around 1648 crore rupees on printing school textbooks for the upcoming academic year 2023.",
        "According to the ministry, 45 percent of the school textbooks required for the new academic year will be printed by the government printing corporation and the remaining 55 percent by private presses.",
        "The Ministry of Education also said that raw paper for printing textbooks will be imported under Indian loan assistance."
      ],
